      "description": "## Initial Release\n\nRun multiple agent CLI sessions (Claude Code, Codex, Gemini, etc.) as tabs within Obsidian.\n\n### Features\n- Multiple simultaneous CLI sessions as Obsidian tabs\n- Configurable CLI profiles (Claude Code, Codex, Gemini, Grok, etc.)\n- Session sidebar with status and notifications\n- Hook notifications via JSONL event file\n- Session resume support\n- Split views, font size controls\n- Ghostty theme support\n- macOS dock badge",
